name: Russia NFT. Pure gold
description: NFT country is Russia.  Made of pure gold, between the gold in the form of the Russian flag is silver, blue emerald and red emerald. The base is made of pure gold of the highest quality 999 samples. The base is made of mahogany, and the upper part of the stand is made of blue emerald. The Russian bear (the symbol of Russia) crawls along the pillar holding the country with the help of a mechanism. The country symbols are also left on the sides of the base with the help of a mechanism: 1. Balalaika (Russian folk instrument) 2. Pokrovsky Cathedral or St. St. Basil's Cathedral 3. Samovar (Wood-burning kettle). 4. Russian hut. A Matryoshka doll rolls back and forth on the back wall of the base.
